h anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus vs Sampdoria 23h00 ng\u00e0y 154 Serie A 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/juventus-sampdoria.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus vs Sampdoria</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh</span><span><span><span> </span>Juventus vs Sampdoria: 4-2<br>\r\n</span></span></h2>\r\n<br>\r\nJuve \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c h\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 su\u00fdt t\u1ea1o ra cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Champions League. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu suy ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 L\u00e3o phu nh\u00e2n m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Sampdoria th\u00ec th\u1ef1c sai l\u1ea7m. X\u01b0a nay, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i Champions League hay d\u1edf ra sao, th\u00ec \u0111\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Juve t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Champions League s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn con \u201cqu\u00e1i v\u1eadt\u201d Juve tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 khi v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Tuy nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 nh\u01b0 \u0103n k\u1eb9o cho Juve, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o HLV Massimiliano Allegri c\u0169ng t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Bianconeri. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 nh\u00e2n Leonardo Bonucci ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf v\u00f2ng 30, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ee1 d\u1ecbp ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf Serie A m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Juve \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ea5t mong manh. 3 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Juve \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 6 b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid (4) v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00f3t b\u1ea3ng Serie A - Benevento (2). Vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n an to\u00e0n c\u0169ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec Juve th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Sampdoria \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tuy\u1ec7t hay c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, h\u1ecd d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i 90 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juve. Nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Marco Giampaolo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. 10 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Samp ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00fang 2 l\u1ea7n.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebft tha v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau d\u1ef1 Europa League, Sampdoria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u1ecfng ch\u00e2n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0 L\u00e3o phu nh\u00e2n, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh t\u1edbi m\u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 tin Sampdoria s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n8 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Sampdoria tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Juve \u0111\u00e3 ghi c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 24 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, t\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh 3 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn. D\u00f9 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Sampdoria \u0111\u00eam nay, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 vua Serie A 6 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Juve gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u00e0n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nJuventus: V\u1eafng Bernardeschi, Barzagli v\u00e0 De Sciglio do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\nSampdoria: Murru ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Bereszynski b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Juventus th\u1eafng 13, thua 3/16 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y; th\u1eafng 8, thua 3/11 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. <br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Sampdoria th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 1, thua 3/5 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua; th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 1, thua 6/10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\n3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Juventus, 5/6 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Sampdoria v\u00e0 6/7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean t\u1ea1i Turin \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean. Juve g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t c\u1edfi m\u1edf, tin cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u01b0a g\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1211","checkdouble":"184303"},{"date":"09:29 15/04","title":"HAGL thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC l\u00e0 v\u00ec b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/15/hagl-thua-sai-gon-fc-la-vi-bau-duc.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articler