u1ed1c n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch trong t\u1ed1p 2 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, HLV Klopp nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i sau m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Sane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 &nbsp;&lsquo;\u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng&rsquo;. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth do Bongda24h.vn t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft l\u1ea1i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. Mohamed Salah &ndash; \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Man City \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League 2017/18 h\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n qua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Bournemouth.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 diem nhan noi bat o tran Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth hinh anh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/diem-nhan-liverpool-30-bournemouth.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alexander-Arnold, Salah d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m75 v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Asmir Begovic \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi, n\u00e2ng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ean 2-0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 30 t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u1ee7a Salah trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap anh b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Harry Kane trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi NHA. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man xanh, Kane l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m Salah t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Salah c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Chi\u1ebfc Gi\u00e0y V\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi 60 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Messi, Lewandowski l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 2 v\u00e0 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. Mane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mane t\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal \u0111ang ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, v\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 7 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (Vong 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (V\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Liverpool-v-AFC-Bournemouth-Premier-League.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mane t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau th\u1eddi gian g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Mane s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 10 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. T\u1eeb pha treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Jordan Henderson b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, Sane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn Begovic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft d\u00ednh b\u00f3ng. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal \u0111\u00e3 \u1eadp v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Mane c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o gi\u00fap HLV Klopp an t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong b\u00e0i to\u00e1n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi chia l\u1eeda tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Salah, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Champions League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Arnold&nbsp;c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 World Cup 2018<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alexander-Arnold \u0111ang s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. V\u1edbi nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i kh\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin c\u1ee7a HLV Klopp v\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Liverpool b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (Vong 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (V\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Premier-League-Liverpool-vs-AFC-Bournemouth-(1).jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sao&nbsp;&nbsp;tr\u1ebb&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alexander-Arnold \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1ea1i&nbsp;</span>Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian qua</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Arnold c\u0169ng tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Salah ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 30 t\u1ea1i Premier League. Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arnold c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Nga \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u00f9ng Tam S\u01b0 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 quan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y Kyle Walker&nbsp;v\u1eabn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate, tuy nhi\u00ean trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u1ea3 Nathaniel Clyne v\u00e0 Joe Gomez \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Alexander-Arnold ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i cho \u0110T Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Jordan Henderson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Man City nh\u01b0ng Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng Jordan Henderson s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 ni\u1ec1m tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, Henderson \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Mane m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Henderson v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 khi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat khi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 27.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (Vong 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (V\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/Premier-League-Liverpool-vs-AFC-Bournemouth.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Henderson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>5. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dejan Lovrens<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7 Liverpool \u1edf v\u00f2ng 34 NHA c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu Dejan Lovrens kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u1edf ph\u00fat 83, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi Ragnar Klavan.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (Vong 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (V\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/4B291B0900000578-5616665-image-a-257_1523744066449.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Dejan Lovrens khi\u1ebfn HLV Klopp lo ng\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Klopp c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i cho t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lovrens khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n g\u1ea7n 10 ng\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Roma \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Lovrens s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Livepool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, d\u0129 nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 bi\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1eafp x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Klopp t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Joel Matip g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf trung t\u00e2m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh ta v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\r\n<strong><em>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Liverpool 3-0 Bournemouth (V\u00f2ng 34 Premier League 2017/18)</em></strong></p>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_266512\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/15/highlight-liverpool-vs-bournemouth-vong-34-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&#10;Roboto;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pha-luoi-bournemouth-salah-tiep-tuc-lap-them-ky-luc-172-184272.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/pha-luoi-bournemouth-salah-tiep-tuc-lap-them-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pha-luoi-bournemouth-salah-tiep-tuc-lap-them-ky-luc-172-184272.html\">Ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Bournemouth, Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1eadp th\u00eam nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nSalah l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bournemouth v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat 69. Anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 30 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u00e0nh t\u00edch...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1208","checkdouble":"184283"},{"date":"10:00 15/04","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Antonio Rudiger v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p southampton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/tai-sao-antonio-rudiger-vang-mat-o-tran-gap-southampton.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.articlerelate2>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate2>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration