e \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m Gary Cahill, Andreas Christensen v\u00e0 Cesar Azpilicueta, trung v\u1ec7 Antonio Rudiger b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte phat bieu ve Antonio Rudiger hinh anh\" title=\"Antonio Conte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Rudiger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/Antonio-Conte-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Rudiger-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rudiger v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Southampton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nVi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u00ednh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Rudiger, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Southampton ghi 2 b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i 3-2. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-southampton-vs-chelsea-tran-dau-vong-34-ngoai-hang-anh-201718-172-184237.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Southampton vs Chelsea</strong></span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Conte n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Rudiger</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Antonio Conte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Rudiger, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte phat bieu ve Antonio Rudiger\" title=\"Conte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Rudiger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/tai-sao-antonio-rudiger-vang-mat-o-tran-gap-southampton.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Antonio Conte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Rudiger</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng d\u00ednh m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o c\u1ea3, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. Rudiger \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 trong tay nhi\u1ec1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00e2n phi\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ecd. M\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c nhau, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi ai c\u1ea3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Southampton, HLV Conte chia s\u1ebb: \u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p 1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1207","checkdouble":"184291"},{"date":"09:38 15/04","title":"Newcastle vs Arsenal (19h30 ng\u00e0y 15/04): \u0110\u1eebng \u0111\u00f9a v\u1edbi \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/newcastle-vs-arsenal-19h30-ngay-1504-dung-dua-voi-chich-choe.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#