xt-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U 1-2 Sevilla\" title=\"M.U 1-2 Sevilla\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/mu-se-khong-the-dua-ve-nhung-ngoi-sao-lon-o-he-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/manchester-united-1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U </strong></span>coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Man City b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Man \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf Champions League, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 Sevilla lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, M.U c\u00f3 3 danh hi\u1ec7u. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u00e0 Europa League. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh FA Cup. Tuy nhi\u00ean nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Tottenham \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft FA Cup, n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Spurs h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Tottenham v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i, th\u1ebf m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ee9t \u0111i v\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Antonio Valencia ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Valencia phat bieu ve MU\" title=\"Antonio Valencia ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/antonio-valencia-mu-se-thach-thuc-moi-danh-hieu-o-mua-giai-toi.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Antonio Valencia ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. V\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, M.U s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e3 l\u00e2u l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/antonio-valencia-43823.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Valencia </strong></span>chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 M.U, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n FA Cup l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1205","checkdouble":"184297"},{"date":"10:42 15/04","title":"Man City t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/10/19/man-city-tinh-gay-soc-voi-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{bac