der: none\" alt=\"Cuc soc Man City mua Kylian Mbappe o He 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Man City mua Kylian Mbappe \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Cuc-soc-Man-City-mua-Kylian-Mbappe-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG s\u1ebd mua s\u1eafm m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf Champions League \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 PSG th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Emery b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi Emery c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, PSG v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG</strong></span>. Theo Mirror, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p chi ra \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 300 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Mbappe</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p chi ra h\u01a1n 300 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, PSG s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe vs Real\" title=\"Mbappe vs Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/mbappe.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mua Mbappe \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Mirror, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 180 tri\u1ec7u euro. PSG s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Mbappe ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng PSG \u0111ang kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i hy sinh m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn sau. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City mua Kylian Mbappe n\u1ebfu PSG bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPep \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n PSG s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Man City c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00fay Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1204","checkdouble":"184298"},{"date":"08:12 15/04","title":"Atalanta 0-0 Inter Milan: S\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch, Nerazzurri nguy c\u01a1 v\u0103ng Top 4","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/atalanta-00-inter-milan-say-chan-tren-dat-khach-nerazzurri-nguy-co-vang-top-4.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weigh