b>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m hai n\u1eeda theo th\u1eddi gian. Hi\u1ec7p 1, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Atlanta l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i n\u1eafm th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng, b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2 Inter m\u1edbi l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. Sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, Atalanta t\u1ef1 tin d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra, \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Bryan Cristante.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/15/a2723.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Atalanta s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Inter, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9. Perisic l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Inter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Cancelo, \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Inter c\u00e0ng gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 Perisic c\u00e0ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn. Chung cu\u1ed9c, hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ket qua Atalanta vs Inter Milan 0-0 tuong thuat Serie A 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Atalanta vs Inter Milan 0-0 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt Serie A 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/inter.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Inter trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Inter \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi 60 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 2 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean l\u00e0 Roma v\u00e0 Lazio nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 tr\u1eadn. T\u1ea1i Serie A th\u00ec 4 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t tham gia gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\nAtalanta: Berisha; Toloi, Caldara, Masiello; Hateboer, De Roon, Freuler, Gosens (Castagne 80); Cristante (Mancini 85); Gomez, Barrow (Cornelius 46)<br>\r\nInter: Handanovic; D'Ambrosio, Skriniar, Miranda, Santon; Gagliardini, Borja Valero (Karamoh 89); Cancelo, Rafinha (Eder 72), Perisic; Icardi.</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1203","checkdouble":"184288"},{"date":"08:33 15/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan vs Napoli 20h00 ng\u00e0y 15/4 (Serie A 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/15/nhan-dinh-ac-milan-vs-napoli-20h00-ngay-154-serie-a-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlere