ead><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhan dinh AC Milan vs Napoli 20h00 ngay 154 Serie A 201718 hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan vs Napoli 20h00 ng\u00e0y 154 Serie A 201718 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/acmilan-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">AC Milan vs Napoli</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh</span><span><span> AC Milan vs Napoli: 0-3<br>\r\n</span></span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMilan t\u1eebng c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian bay cao v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Gattuso. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Europa League th\u00ec Rossoneri \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t. B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Milan ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Sassuolo th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1. N\u00ean nh\u1edb, Sassuolo ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i BXH nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn Rossoneri to\u00e1t m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi Kalinic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro \u1edf ph\u00fat 86. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nMilan t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Juventus. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3. Tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea1nh tranh Top 4 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Gattuso. 3 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 4/9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i. H\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 Milan b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 52 \u0111i\u1ec3m/31 v\u00f2ng, k\u00e9m nh\u00f3m 4 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadn 8 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Milan c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong Top 4 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, Rossoneri t\u1ed1i nay c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Hai trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Bonucci v\u00e0 Romagnoli \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Napoli v\u00ec b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1eafng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e9p n\u00e0y, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Milan s\u1ebd y\u1ebfu \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ebd l\u1ed9 ra khi Milan ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Napoli. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Napoli v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo. Ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng v\u00e0i ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Napoli \u0111\u00e3 ghi li\u1ec1n 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Napoli ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng mong manh trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Scudetto. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 san l\u1ea5p trong 7 v\u00f2ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Napoli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 66 b\u00e0n \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t Milan ngay t\u1ea1i San Siro. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\nMilan th\u1eafng 10, thua 8/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Milan c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\n11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Napoli c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <br>\r\nNapoli th\u1eafng 5, thua 13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Milan c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1. 11/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Napoli c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. NHM n\u00ean \u0111\u1ee3i sau 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1202","checkdouble":"184290"},{"date":"07:57 15/04","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/15/thay-gi-sau-chien-thang-bat-ngo-cua-sai-gon-fc-truoc-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6px;min-height:72px}div.