Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Barca t\u1ecf ra r\u1eddi r\u1ea1c. Ch\u00ednh Valencia m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i s\u1eafc n\u00e9t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y nguy hi\u1ec3m. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Goncalo Guedes v\u00e0 Rodrigo c\u1ee7a B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh Barca. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ter Stegen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez mo ty so cho Barca\" title=\"Suarez mo ty so cho Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Suarez-mo-ty-so-cho-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suarez m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, Barca nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Valencia. Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho, Luis Suarez v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Barca ph\u00fat 15. 1-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, nhu\u1ec7 kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a Valencia suy gi\u1ea3m h\u1eb3n. Barca b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u song c\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n l\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. Nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 51, Samuel Umtiti nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Barca nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng Andres Iniesta hay Denis Suarez ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Valencia, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Umtiti ghi ban thu 2 cho Barca\" title=\"Umtiti ghi ban thu 2 cho Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Umtiti-ghi-ban-thu-2-cho-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Umtiti ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 87, pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n n\u00f4n n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. T\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly 11m, Dani Parejo r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng 1-2 cho Valencia b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Ter Stegen \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng. Trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng song B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Barca. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Blaugrana \u0111\u00fat t\u00fai 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat 2-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBarcelona: </strong>Ter Stegen, Pique,Umtiti, Alba, Roberto, Busquets, Paulinho, Iniesta (D.Suarez 84'), Coutinho (Dembele 79'), L.Suarez, Messi.<br>\r\n<strong>Valencia: </strong>Neto, Garay, Vezo, Gabriel, Gaya, Guedes (Pereira 69'), Kondogbia, Pareno, Soler, Rodrigo (Zaza 80'), Mina (Vietto 71').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Barca vs Valencia\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/14/Thong-tin-sau-tran-Barca-vs-Valencia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia (v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga 2017/18):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/14/Highlight-Barca-vs-Valencia-vong-32-La-Liga.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\