dd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 39 t\u00ednh t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Barca \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i La Liga, ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Sociedad thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp m\u00f9a 1979/80. M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng thua c\u1ee7a Blaugrana kh\u1edfi ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi 7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Luis Enrique v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebf t\u1ee5c b\u1edfi Ernesto Valverde.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde phat bieu sau tran Barca vs Valencia hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Barca vs Valencia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/HLV-Valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Barca-vs-Valencia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barcelona \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Valencia 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 32 v\u00f2ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Barca ch\u01b0a thua v\u1edbi 25 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 7 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. H\u1ecd h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valverde kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Barca vs Valencia l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1 cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca. Theo nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 54 tu\u1ed5i, quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c thua 0-3 Roma h\u1ed3i gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde\" title=\"HLV Valverde\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Barca vs Valencia l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan t\u00e2m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c&rdquo;, Valverde n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u1eafm, c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean sau m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc 6 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t vui khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng to l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Valencia (V\u00f2ng 32 La Liga):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/14/Highlight-Barca-vs-Valencia-vong-32-La-Liga.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-barca-21-valencia-vong-32-la-liga-201718-328-184269.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Barca 2-1 Valencia (V\u00f2ng 32 La Liga 2017/18)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ket-qua-barca-vs-valencia-tran-dau-vong-32-la-liga-201718-180-184252.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Barca vs Valencia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 32 La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-valencia-21h15-ngay-144-la-liga-201718-372-184239.html\">Barca 2-1 Valencia (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div cl