olor:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, sau khi thua nh\u1ee5c nh\u00e3 Roma v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-3, qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Champions League b\u1edfi lu\u1eadt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 La Liga, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ernesto Valverde tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Valencia. H\u1ecd d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n do c\u00f4ng Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti, c\u00f2n b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi Parejo nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00fap Barca v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd ch\u1ea1m m\u1ed1c 39 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf La Liga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV Valverde cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed xung quanh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m, b\u1edfi v\u1eady 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00f4m nay gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde noi gi sau tran thang Valencia hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Ernesto Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Valencia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/15/barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HV Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Barca 2-1 Valencia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi ch\u1eb3ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u00ean sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn \u0111\u00f3 (thua AS Roma). Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i sau l\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Barcelona c\u0169ng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Cup Nh\u00e0 vua, khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Sevilla.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Ernesto Valverde ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. &ldquo;Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1eb7m nh\u1ea5m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t tinh th\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00f3?&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd chui trong b\u1ecdc 3 th\u00e1ng? Kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n th\u1ee9c d\u1eady v\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi 2 danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga v\u00e0 Cup Nh\u00e0 vua. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 Barcelona vs Valencia 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/12055718/013100\" target=\"_blank\">Barca 2-1 Valencia<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/4/14/Highlight-Barca-vs-Valencia-vong-32-La-Liga.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia-180-184271.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/15/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-sau-tran-barca-vs-valencia-180-184271.html\">HLV Valverde b\u00e0ng quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca</span><br>\r\nBarcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Valencia 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp n\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i La Liga. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Barca vs Valencia l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y quan...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"1192","checkdouble":"184280"}]}